features: Innovative 3-in-1 solution allows you to pack either one large checked piece of luggage or two smaller carry-ons
Easy to pack and stay organized with a spacious interior that divides into two separate compartments or opens into one large packing space
Smooth and easy transport with tough, oversized wheels and V-Tubing telescoping handles
Effortless travel thanks to the piggyback strap attachment loop that allows an additional bag to be hooked on
Bag design absorbs the impact of travel due to the durable exoskeleton and molded polycarbonate back panel
Separate your shoes and dirty laundry from other belongings in the multi-purpose compartment
Smooth lifting and rearranging in overhead bins with top, side and bottom grab handles
Keep belongings in place throughout travel due to external compression straps
Quick access to keys, wallet and smaller items through zippered mesh pocket
Built in ID card slot simplifies identification of bag
